This paper deals with versioning of ontologies, which is a topic that falls under the umbrella of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper specifically focuses on the lightweight description logic EL, which is a subfield of logic (cs.LO). The algorithms presented in the paper involve computation and manipulation of data, which is a topic in databases (cs.DB) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper also deals with queries and their answers, which is a topic in natural language processing and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
